      "file_path": "models/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/clamp/controlloop/models/messages/dmaap/participant/ParticipantStatus.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 54,
      "message": "Map will be the choice here.\nparticipantDefinitionUpdateMap as defined in the Wiki needs a External Map with ParticipantId as Key, and the value of the external map\nis also a Map (ControlLoopElementDefintionMap), which has several ControlLoopElementDefinitions keyed with Control Loop Element Definition ID\n\nReference from wiki:\nParticipantDefinitionUpdateMap\tMap with Participant ID as its key, each value on the map is a ControlLoopElementDefintionMap\nControlLoopElementDefintionMap\tList of ControlLoopElementDefinition values for a particular participant, keyed by its Control Loop Element Definition ID\nControlLoopElementDefinition\tA ControlLoopElementToscaServiceTemplate containing the definition of the Control Loop Element and a CommonPropertiesMap with the values of the common property values for Control Loop Elements of this type\nControlLoopElementToscaServiceTemplate\tThe definition of the Control Loop Element in TOSCA\nCommonPropertiesMap\tA <String, String> map indexed by the property name. Each map entry is the serialized value of the property, which can be deserialized into an instance of the type of the property.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 7504,
        "name": "Sirisha Manchikanti",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "sirisha.manchikanti@est.tech",
        "username": "Sirisha_Manchikanti"
      },
      "updated": "2021-08-04 13:49:09.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "f04cff0a_4c0d2a5c",
      "unresolved": true
    },
